<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٨٢ - <span class="c2">(٢٥١٤)</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6669">هَدَّابُ بْنُ خَالِدٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2636">سُلَيْمَانُ بْنُ الْمُغِيرَةِ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1663">حُمَيْدُ بْنُ هِلَالٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3715">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ الصَّامِتِ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1181">أَبُو ذَرٍّ </a>: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٧٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5"><span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">« غِفَارُ غَفَرَ اللهُ لَهَا، وَأَسْلَمُ سَالَمَهَا اللهُ »</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>